-/*
- * Warning:
+/**
+ * text_poke_early - Update instructions on a live kernel at boot time
+ * @addr: address to modify
+ * @opcode: source of the copy
+ * @len: length to copy
+ *
  * When you use this code to patch more than one byte of an instruction
